\newlabel{fig:plot2}{{4}{9}{Weight evolution over iterations. Top-left: intercept $a_0$ converges to $\approx -1.4 \times 10^{-16}$ (effectively zero after normalization). Top-right: slope $a_1$ converges to $\approx 0.707$. Bottom: 2D weight-space trajectory showing both algorithms trace the same path from $[0, 0]$ to the optimum}{figure.caption.8}{}}
